Aluminum Co of Canada Ltd, a unit ofAlcan Aluminium Ltd, said it began an offer of 400,000 sharesof a new series of preferred stock after its board approved thefinal prospectus.    The offering, which is being made in Canada, is for 400,000shares of cumulative redeemable retractable preference sharesat 25 dlrs apiece.    The quarterly dividend on the stock, to be known as seriesF, will be 50 cts Canadian, equal to eight pct a year, thecompany said. Reuter&#3;